Agar aap pip install streamlit karte hain, toh Streamlit system-wide install ho jata hai aur kisi bhi Python project mein use kiya ja sakta hai.

Lekin agar aap uv ya virtual environment use karna chahtay hain, toh aap sirf us specific project ke andar streamlit install kar sakte hain, bina system-wide install kiye.

ðŸ”¹ Comparison: pip install vs uv
Method	Scope	Usage
pip install streamlit	System-wide	Har project mein use ho sakta hai
uv pip install streamlit	Project-specific	Sirf usi project mein chalega
Agar aap ek specific project ke andar Streamlit install karna chahte hain toh uv ya virtual environment (venv) ka use karna behtar hoga.